hyp2mat is a utility which converts HyperLynx files to CSXCAD for electromagnetic simulation, or to PDF for printing.
hyp2mat is distributed with openEMS, an electromagnetic field solver. See http://www.openems.de

Tested on Linux ubuntu, MacOSX and Windows/MingW.

See the file 'INSTALL' for compilation instructions.
Alternatively, pre-compiled binaries are available.
Windows binaries can be downloaded from http://www.kdvelectronics.eu/hyp2mat/hyp2mat-win32-current.zip .
Linux packages can be downloaded from https://build.opensuse.org/package/show?package=hyp2mat&project=home%3Asibbi77
